description: When you need just a little more distance, USB cable designed to work with an iPad, iPhone or iPod  this cable will extend the reach of your USB A/B cable. Foil and braid shielding reduce EMI/RFI interference and twisted pair construction helps reduce crosstalk for a high-speed, error-free data transfer. USB 2.0 compatible. PC and Mac® compatible. Lifetime Warranty.
title: C2G / Cables to Go 26686 USB 2.0 Cable for iPod/iPhone/iPad A Male to A Female Extension Cable, White (3 Meters/9.84 Feet)
